{
  "stem": "7160.1",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we have to walk to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it's about 950 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave us one loaf of bread and about a liter of [? hank. ?] And that's gonna to be the food for the-- we don't know what-- if-- if this was for one day, or if it's gonna be for, [LAUGHS] you know, for the whole transport.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't even know how many days it was gonna be on the road.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was so hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I ate everything in one day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I want to drink.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no water to drink.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're going crazy-- the [? salt ?] [? hank. ?] So we start walking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're walking, and put in the line, and keep us walking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "About a couple of-- about 100 miles from Warsaw was a big river.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know the name of the river.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think it's the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm not sure-- a very big river-- I would say maybe about 300, 400 feet wide.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There-- and they make us to cross.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They don't want us to go on top on in the-- in the brick over there, because they had the machine guns on top-- the-- the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So some of us didn't know how to swim.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not everybody knew how to swim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the river, it was kind of beginning of winter, even block of ice still was flowing on top in the river there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can see the-- so-- so then the SS tell 'em go in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anybody who won't go in, they start shooting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was a good swimmer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I learned in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- and I start swimming across the river.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
